title: #92Noon! Florio/Larrivee/Zimmer/Farming
description: Florio kicks off the show, followed by Packers voice Wayne Larrivee. The TitleTown podcast finishes the first hour. Mike Zimmer presser and opinions, opens up final hour to celebrating farmers and more football conversation!
